java program with array dequeue
==============================

package Collections;

import java.util.ArrayDeque;

public class ArrayDequeDemo {
	
	public static void main(String[] args) {
		
		
		ArrayDeque<String> ad = new ArrayDeque<>();
		
		ad.add("one");
		ad.add("two");
		ad.add("three");
		ad.addFirst("sonu");
		
		
		
		System.out.println(ad);
		
		ad.pollFirst();
		System.out.println(ad);
		ad.pollLast();
		System.out.println(ad);
	}

}



OUTPUT:
=======

[sonu, one, two, three]
[one, two, three]
[one, two]









